properties.name: Madness Unveiled
properties.description:
In a forgotten dungeon, an archaeologist uncovers ancient secrets. As you explore, darkness takes hold, transforming you from an explorer to a warrior. Madness lurks, consuming your mind. Confront bosses, unearth artifacts, unleash forbidden powers. Survive the descent, escape Madness Unveiled.

Due to browser restriction:
1. Refresh the page before clicking "Continue" in Main Menu.
2. Exit Game does not work.

*This is a collaborative project developed as coursework*
